he-triangle/adjvjslacjskclklkxlc-learning-to-love-duke-basketball/" class="pullFull"><img src="https://espngrantland.files.wordpress.com/2015/04/duke-okafor-tri1-e1428020903795.jpg?w=300" /></a><p class="byline category"><a href="http://grantland.com/tags/2015-ncaa-tournament/">2015 NCAA Tournament</a></p><h3><a name="&amp;lpos=grantlandSiteNav&amp;lid=TheTriangle_Story3" href="http://grantland.com/the-triangle/adjvjslacjskclklkxlc-learning-to-love-duke-basketball/">Adjvjslacjskclklkxlc: Learning to Love Duke Basketball</a></h3><p class="summary"></p><div class="byline"><em>by</em> <a class="fn" rel="author" href="http://grantland.com/contributors/brian-phillips/">Brian Phillips</a></div></div></div></div><a href="http://grantland.com/the-triangle/" name="&lpos=grantlandSiteNav&lid=The Triangle" class="see-all"><em>See</em> All The Triangle</a></div>
